{"tid":2507862,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國拉開戰幕 東歐多國接連驅逐俄羅斯外交官出境","createTime":"2021-04-28T09:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T10:21:27.000Z","uid":66087,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5863ca020479ccef51c96923c5eafd1ba9758ae3","tid":2507862,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:55:28.000Z","msg":"2021-04-28 11:25<br />\n<br />\n4月26日羅馬尼亞外交部宣布將俄羅斯駐羅使館副武官阿列克謝&middot;格里沙耶夫列為「不受歡迎的人」，並將其驅逐出境。<br />\n<br />\n斯洛伐克和波羅的海三國&mdash;&mdash;愛沙尼亞、拉脫維亞、立陶宛也宣布將驅逐總共7名俄羅斯外交官。<br />\n<br />\n在這一輪「外交驅逐戰」中，羅馬尼亞是第四個驅逐俄羅斯外交官的東歐國家。在此之前，波蘭、捷克和烏克蘭已經加入了由美國挑頭的「對俄攻勢」。<br />\n<br />\n波蘭外交部15日宣布驅逐3名俄羅斯外交人員，捷克17日宣布驅逐18名俄羅斯外交官，烏克蘭17日也宣布驅逐1名俄羅斯外交官。<br />\n<br />\n這一輪外交驅逐戰的大幕由美國揭開。4月15日，美國政府以俄羅斯進行網路襲擊、干預美國選舉等「惡意活動」為由，對俄實施大規模製裁併驅逐10名俄外交人員。美方公佈的具體制裁措施包括禁止美國金融機構參與俄債券及基金投資、對6家俄羅斯科技公司採取制裁行動等。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，在本輪風波中，緊跟美國步伐驅逐俄外交官的不是西歐國家，而是一些東歐國家，它們迅速採取了與美方相呼應的行動。<br />\n<br />\n美歐對俄的制裁動作並沒有放緩，俄方也繼續進行反制。當地時間4月27日，俄羅斯外長拉夫羅夫接受俄新社採訪時表示，俄美關係仍在繼續下滑，根源在美方，因為拜登政府仍在延續前兩屆美國政府的對俄政策。"},{"pid":"24e3df996aeacee7c3e4a1d3dcd9f26be628b893","tid":2507862,"uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:56:27.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯同西方關係差唔多玩完了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac569ea2def9f0b443f2808611f40e4f8aa9a4b1","tid":2507862,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24e3df996aeacee7c3e4a1d3dcd9f26be628b893","tid":2507862,"uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:56:27.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯同西方關係差唔多玩完了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:57:56.000Z","msg":"西歐要俄佬石油<br />\n如果真係出事<br />\n佢哋先係大輸家"},{"pid":"89330368684e42f5da81b49151710cd2fd22f5b8","tid":2507862,"uid":231480,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bwqnK83.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbwqnK83.gif&h=d3e4be6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10dcc5e3aca61300df7adc20941bbc92982b7cf3","tid":2507862,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:59:53.000Z","msg":"繼續逼中俄合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1046ba7a09d8eb2deccc27f5c56534ee452d0d","tid":2507862,"uid":130456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:08:27.000Z","msg":"其實唔明 點解美帝要突然辣兩條火頭 打俄同支那？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6ff294f919bf60cd71b9e88fd4d1b2383be61a","tid":2507862,"uid":198181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:20:37.000Z","msg":"敗登打俄佬，放生支那畜牲囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274487cd95dad631b928f0a0308fe9ce088eba07","tid":2507862,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b1046ba7a09d8eb2deccc27f5c56534ee452d0d","tid":2507862,"uid":130456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:08:27.000Z","msg":"其實唔明 點解美帝要突然辣兩條火頭 打俄同支那？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:20:46.000Z","msg":"同問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e7289940baca33e773b16306ccf7f27c9d47dd","tid":2507862,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10dcc5e3aca61300df7adc20941bbc92982b7cf3","tid":2507862,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:59:53.000Z","msg":"繼續逼中俄合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:21:27.000Z","msg":"擺明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係點賺人民幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/no